470
00:42:46,250 --> 00:42:48,600
Où est mon collier ?

471
00:42:51,200 --> 00:42:53,960
Je dois lui parler.

472
00:42:54,470 --> 00:42:56,750
Vite.

473
00:42:56,750 --> 00:42:58,960
