556
00:49:03,750 --> 00:49:06,600
- Nous sommes arrivés.
 - Oui. Nous y sommes.

557
00:49:10,360 --> 00:49:11,770
Je vais rentrer.

558
00:49:11,770 --> 00:49:14,730
Oui. Vas-y.

559
00:49:14,730 --> 00:49:16,300
Attends.

560
00:49:20,050 --> 00:49:22,090
Dors bien.

